{"tid":896411,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"曾蔭權:4000蚊呎仲有好多","createTime":"2018-11-10T04:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T06:35:34.000Z","uid":73092,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cebf92ee34800929f950992028e7fe1e21c05a98","tid":896411,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"近期本港樓市熾熱，豪宅呎價更創全球紀錄，市民抱怨樓價高、炒風盛，專業中產人士也投訴無力負擔買樓，不過特首曾蔭權視若無睹，反叫市民不要「太揀擇」，可購買地區偏遠及小型單位，「4,000蚊一呎嘅仲有好多。」有立法會議員警告曾蔭權要趁樓價尚未升至97年水平時，以溫和措施壓抑樓價，否則只會令市民的不滿升溫。<br />\n<br />\n曾蔭權前日在施政報告記者會揚言，「豪宅樓價不會影響民生」，多名市民昨日於電台聯播施政報告節目中反擊，指現時樓價過高，一般市民根本負擔不起。夫婦月入30,000元的李先生批評：「家啲樓太貴，坐底都二、三百萬，我想問點樣令到我哋呢班人可以置業？」另一聽眾鄭先生直斥：「家樓價好多人都覺得脫節，市面價錢好離譜！」<br />\n<br />\n中產：俾大陸人搶貴晒<br />\n<br />\n有專業中產人士也投訴買不到樓，任職醫生的聽眾嚴小姐原計劃明年與任職律師的男友置業結婚，她指現時樓價太貴，無力供樓，「樓市應該㩒吓，家樓市連專業人士都冇可能供得起，貴成咁，係咪矯枉過正？」她更道出不少中產人士心聲，「中產冇要求政府做啲乜，自力更生，但係買樓方面，俾大陸人搶貴晒，香港啲人點呢？」她要求當局調整內地人來港的投資政策，保障港人置業權益。<br />\n<br />\n不過，曾蔭權仍「死撐」，指本港豪宅與一般樓宇屬不同市場，近日以天價成交的豪宅單位對一般市民影響不大，「樓價呢段時間係微升，但同97、98年仲有差距。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">曾蔭權更以過來人身份稱，當年自己結婚後都是租樓，等到30多歲才置業，「我哋唔好為幾多錢一呎，60,000蚊一呎，70,000蚊一呎而影響我哋呢樣嘢，你打開張報紙睇，4,000蚊一呎嘅都仲有好多&hellip;&hellip;最緊要唔好突然跌，影響購買能力。」他着市民不要太揀擇，可購買地區偏遠及小型單位。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，聽眾王小姐踢爆曾蔭權「豪宅樓價不會影響民生」說法，指其原租住40年樓齡的新界區樓宇，近日被炒至400萬元，業主為出售單位，迫她搬遷，「房地產唔係特首你話唔好炒到70,000蚊一呎，而係成個香港每日都被不明來歷嘅錢破壞得好緊要。」曾蔭權只重申，政府不能以有形之手控制樓市，令樓市大上大落。<br />\n<br />\n市區單位　選擇極少<br />\n<br />\n本報以400至700呎的中小型單位，並以200萬至400萬元的售價尋找，發現4,000元以下呎價的單位大部份位處新界區，可供選擇的港九市區單位極少（見表）。<br />\n民主黨立法會議員李永達指曾蔭權對高樓價袖手旁觀，等於引火自焚，最終重演「八萬五」，令不少業主淪為負資產人士。<br />\n<br />\n李永達認為，政府要趁樓價尚未升到97年水平，先行以較溫和措施壓抑樓價上升，包括恢復定期賣地，重建有限數目的居屋，否則任由情況發展下去，只會令市民不滿繼續升溫。<br />\n<br />\n本港十大屋苑平均呎價<br />\n太古城　 $7,739<br />\n康怡花園　 $6,185<br />\n杏花邨　 $5,947<br />\n海怡半島　 $5,814<br />\n黃埔花園　 $5,490<br />\n滙景花園　 $5,213<br />\n麗港城　 $4,922<br />\n沙田第一城　 $4,611<br />\n美孚新邨　 $4,107<br />\n嘉湖山莊　 $2,145<br />\n註：呎價為09年10月最新數字<br />\n<br />\n 將軍澳新寶城<br />\n將軍澳新寶城<br />\n呎價 $4000以下部份屋苑<br />\n屯門卓爾居　 $3,400<br />\n荃灣麗城花園　 $3,472<br />\n東涌藍天海岸　 $3,472<br />\n青衣海欣花園　 $3,512<br />\n上水皇府山　 $3,875<br />\n長沙灣悅海軒　 $3,905<br />\n鴨脷洲景惠花園　 $3,969<br />\n將軍澳海悅豪園　 $3,979<br />\n將軍澳新寶城　 $3,980<br />\n註：以上單位面積為400至700平方呎、售價200萬至400萬<br />\n資料來源：中原地產"},{"pid":"0f4c915b29b57fe80d8a945123377dbe34cb76ec","tid":896411,"uid":23923,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"09年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0919df97f8231d7a8a215600dd8f9bfec3f333c","tid":896411,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f4c915b29b57fe80d8a945123377dbe34cb76ec","tid":896411,"uid":23923,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"09年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:11:59.000Z","msg":"樓爆緊，要提下大家唔好入市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b3bb5c4e4f953213e0f5e171e2dfad8d3efa19","tid":896411,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"又真係有好多 <br />\n當時有翻咁上下投資 依㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fde4076aa0dcbf437bf934aad940929d7c540e","tid":896411,"uid":155225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"呢件垃圾正仆街，快d死"},{"pid":"e1115461d2be413868f09102e01968a15748466b","tid":896411,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"一早又唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc675a64bf33250941088210d14d25f258ffb290","tid":896411,"uid":190540,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"268d860fc1e14deb87857314f1bd2936d134db05","tid":896411,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06cda5fd809f8d38b112cee7ea8eb42586f04c42","tid":896411,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:11:18.000Z","msg":"而家興440萬買都叫好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfbecea9a41da5acfcb90e9ec878b78df55b1d9","tid":896411,"uid":102179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"原來講撚左十年政府都係乜都做唔撚到"},{"pid":"51111bdb2b07271c7e9d647bfb0c3d8556b7259d","tid":896411,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc675a64bf33250941088210d14d25f258ffb290","tid":896411,"uid":190540,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】政府推出大學畢業生實習計劃，讓僱主可以不低於四千元聘請大學畢業生，聲言相信僱主最終提供的薪酬會遠高於四千元。勞工及福利局局長張建宗昨宣布，自計劃於本月初公開邀請機構參與以來，已接到近二千個本港及內地的職位空缺，平均月薪為九千元。不過，在約一千六百個本港職位中，約三十個月薪屬「四千元左右」，佔總空缺百分之二；亦有二十至三十個月薪只得六千元，部分學生仍然無可避免要做廉價勞工。"},{"pid":"bfc7754a603e2727a61425f0bd83bb8be540bb1f","tid":896411,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:16:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3cd017b5923173b84f1f0364b1dbf1ac0dfe9e0","tid":896411,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:17:19.000Z","msg":"香港柒野建築面積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23230dde09fc602248029f5fc309e77546c2fe35","tid":896411,"uid":196712,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d7a40ba63dde526f720eb5a44c10af5ba3f22f4","tid":896411,"uid":6297,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"停賣地停建居屋唔開發土地停收地，曾蔭權最後下場就係用幾千萬打官司，臨老入監房，身敗名裂！"},{"pid":"8f1877294077ae9766c51b4b0ada87c6aeb3dc6a","tid":896411,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:35:26.000Z","msg":"09年嘅貨先係正價"},{"pid":"54f664d447ab6b979c2059e4b0380dc865431f78","tid":896411,"uid":80072,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔撚好再講以前點買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲老屎忽真係好戇鳩"},{"pid":"9443dcdf2bf75cc391e0d47b1c31ff741d559873","tid":896411,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"唐唐個陣叫人返龍華住香港返工添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac669799a8f8c5e8b8f0ddb46eb251f5ae49da6d","tid":896411,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42fde4076aa0dcbf437bf934aad940929d7c540e","tid":896411,"uid":155225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"呢件垃圾正仆街，快d死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"未死得，牠仲上緊訴，有機會唔駛再坐監、恢復頭銜"},{"pid":"2d63cec3e2ac2cc019bbb8d9001cfb50a9a93e59","tid":896411,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"之前仲有班賤種話曾蔭權好好<br />\n黃種賤畜果種賤格真係賤到入心"}]}